    "name": "Echoes of Mora",
    "steam_appid": 3129050,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129050/extras/d6b5f88ff7e10f6833e3d1e28853d4f1.poster.avif?t=1772026744\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129050/extras/d6b5f88ff7e10f6833e3d1e28853d4f1.webm?t=1772026744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《莫拉之声》（Echoes of Mora） 将潜入神秘水下世界的幻想变为现实。畅游在被洪水淹没多年的村庄中，探索尘封的秘密并揭开这神秘故事背后的面纱。加入年轻的莫拉，踏上跨越时空的旅程，寻找她失踪的兄弟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129050/extras/15ebf153bbb3f9658f8dd803b6afa8df.webp?t=1772026744\" width=616 height=39 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129050/extras/a3d4bdc39d840f65b69598946bd7bcd2.poster.avif?t=1772026744\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129050/extras/a3d4bdc39d840f65b69598946bd7bcd2.webm?t=1772026744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找关于村庄的线索，解开谜题，并找到“回声”。它将带你回到洪水来临之前的时刻。在这些时间传送门中，你能看到灾难前的村庄美景，听到村民的细语交谈，甚至能与莫拉互动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自从哥哥消失在被诅咒的紫色湖畔后，莫拉决定踏上征途，找回自己所珍爱的人。但随着湖水不断上涨并威胁着整个村庄，你的帮助在此时至关重要。快去水下世界中分享你找到的线索，引导过去的莫拉，并陪伴她踏上一段可能改变洪水命运的时空之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129050/extras/6e421bba98774e802364cc448012af2d.webp?t=1772026744\" width=616 height=39 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129050/extras/ad453cec618019cba35477d92447def4.poster.avif?t=1772026744\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129050/extras/ad453cec618019cba35477d92447def4.webm?t=1772026744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可流畅探索沉没的海洋景观，并享受与环境的丰富互动体验。支持PC端键盘、鼠标或手柄操作，亦可选择通过动作追踪实现自然手臂划水动作的沉浸式VR体验。随时无缝切换模式，让你自由选择探索水下世界的途径。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129050/extras/a1260be45e54af48b249fa0b98bdb672.poster.avif?t=1772026744\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129050/extras/a1260be45e54af48b249fa0b98bdb672.webm?t=1772026744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129050/extras/38e3dee7f6763b28193d9789cb1c9d38.webp?t=1772026744\" width=616 height=39 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索引人入胜的水下世界，体验一段关于兄妹情感的动人故事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >趣味十足的环境谜题，找寻“回声”穿越时空，收集隐藏线索，最终揭开莫拉哥哥失踪的真相</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获得直接与过去的莫拉互动的能力，影响村庄的命运与被洪水淹没的灾难</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持键盘/鼠标或手柄在PC端游玩；兼容VR设备，带来沉浸式体验</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在同一游戏会话中随时无缝切换PC与VR模式</p></li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 德语, 韩语, 波兰语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 乌克兰语, 法语, 意大利语, 繁体中文, 简体中文, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 泰语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
